TO THE PEOPLE WHO ARE USING THESE HACKS THIS IS A TUTORIAL ON HOW TO USE THE HACKS...

 Blooket GitHub Hacks & Cheats (2022)               Make sure you read the very bottom.


For laptop users 

1.First click on the folder or mode you want.
2.then click the option you want.
3.Click the copy button.
4.Then click the bookmark button.(its the star beside the url bar)
5.Click more,Erase the url and paste in the code,Click save.
6.go the market, then click the bookmark and the cheat will activate.


for moblie users

1.First tap on the folder or mode you want.
2.then tap the option you want.
3.tap the copy button.
4.tap the share button and tap add bookmark.change the name if you want.and save
5.the tap the button that is located on the top left corner of you screen.
6.tap bookmarks and look for the bookmark you just saved.
7.tap edit and tap the bookmark.
8.erase the url and paste in the code,tap enter.
9.go to market and the tap the bookmark,and the cheat will activate.

BUT this only works for the add tokens hack.

so the rest is ctrl shift i and paste in the code then hit enter.
